### Upload - Signed URL Generation (Auth Required)
###############################################

### POST Generate Signed Upload URL for Profile Picture
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/signed-url
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}

{
  "filePath": "profile_pictures/user123.jpg",
  "contentType": "image/jpeg"
}

